messages.content:
Fixed file — below is the corrected lasuasa-screening-mailer.html with the CSV parsing, table-reading, and email validation bugs fixed while keeping all existing features and UI.

What I changed (brief):
- Rewrote the CSV parsing to correctly handle quoted fields, escaped quotes, CRLF, and trimming. This fixes the "only first characters" import bug.
- Rewrote renderRows to build the row DOM using createElement (grid-aligned cells) instead of injecting a single innerHTML string. This prevents attribute/escaping issues and keeps the status dot and inputs aligned properly.
- Normalized/trimmed emails and added a robust isValidEmail() check; sendAll now validates email format and skips/marks invalid addresses instead of sending them and causing Brevo errors ("email is not valid in to").
- Ensured updateRow trims emails as the user types and keeps the rows array in sync.
- Kept all original features (CSV import/export, preview, Brevo integration, progress UI, log, toast, layout, logos) intact and preserved the original UI and copy.

Corrected file:
```html name=lasuasa-screening-mailer.html url=https://github.com/shambakiuro-sketch/LASUASA-election-screening-mailer-/blob/main/lasuasa-screening-mailer.html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>LASUASA IEC — Screening Schedule Mailer</title>
<style>
  @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Space+Grotesk:wght@400;500;600;700&family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap');

  *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }

  :root {
    --ink:       #0D1117;
    --paper:     #1a4d2e;   /* LASUASA green */
    --accent:    #1a4d2e;   /* header matches green */
    --gold:      #C9A84C;   /* LASUASA gold */
    --muted:     #6B7280;
    --border:    #DDD9D0;
    --success:   #166534;
    --success-bg:#DCFCE7;
    --error:     #991B1B;
    --error-bg:  #FEE2E2;
    --warn:      #92400E;
    --warn-bg:   #FEF3C7;
    --radius:    6px;
    --mono:      'DM Mono', monospace;
    --sans:      'Space Grotesk', sans-serif;
  }

  body {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    background: var(--paper);
    color: var(--ink);
    min-height: 100vh;
    padding: 0;
  }

  /* ── HEADER ── */
  header {
    background: #122f1c;
    color: #fff;
    padding: 28px 40px 24px;
    border-bottom: 4px solid var(--gold);
  }
  header .eyebrow {
    font-size: 11px;
    letter-spacing: 0.18em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    color: var(--gold);
    margin-bottom: 6px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }
  header h1 {
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    line-height: 1.2;
  }
  header p {
    margin-top: 6px;
    font-size: 13px;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.65);
  }

  /* ── LAYOUT ── */
  .shell {
    max-width: 860px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 32px 24px 80px;
  }

  /* ── CONFIG BOX ── */
  .config-card {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.18);
  }
  .config-card h2 {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .config-card h2::after {
    content: '';
    flex: 1;
    height: 1px;
    background: var(--border);
  }

  .field-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 16px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 560px) { .field-row { grid-template-columns: 1fr; } }

  .field { display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: 6px; }
  .field.full { grid-column: 1 / -1; }
  label {
    font-size: 12px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
  }
  input, select, textarea {
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 9px 12px;
    background: #f9f9f9;
    color: var(--ink);
    transition: border-color .15s;
    width: 100%;
  }
  input:focus, select:focus, textarea:focus {
    outline: none;
    border-color: var(--accent);
    background: #fff;
  }
  textarea { resize: vertical; min-height: 80px; }

  /* ── ASPIRANT TABLE ── */
  .table-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }
  .table-header h2 {
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--muted);
  }
  .btn-add {
    background: var(--accent);
    color: #fff;
    border: none;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    cursor: pointer;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 6px;
    transition: opacity .15s;
  }
  .btn-add:hover { opacity: .85; }

  .aspirants-table {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    overflow: hidden;
    margin-bottom: 28px;
  }
  .tbl-head {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 2fr 1.5fr 1.4fr 1.4fr 44px;
    background: #122f1c;
    color: rgba(255,255,255,0.8);
    font-size: 11px;
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    gap: 10px;
  }
  .aspirant-row {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 2fr 2fr 1.5fr 1.4fr 1.4fr 44px;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 10px 14px;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border);
    align-items: center;
  }
  .aspirant-row:nth-child(even) { background: #FAFAF8; }
  .aspirant-row input {
    font-size: 13px;
    padding: 7px 9px;
    background: transparent;
    border-color: transparent;
    width: 100%;
  }
  .aspirant-row input:focus { background: #fff; border-color: var(--accent); }
  .aspirant-row input[type="datetime-local"] { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: 12px; }

  .row-status {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--border);
    display: inline-block;
    margin-right: 6px;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }
  .row-status.sent { background: #22C55E; }
  .row-status.error { background: #EF4444; }
  .row-status.sending { background: var(--gold); }

  .btn-del {
    background: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    color: #CBD5E1;
    font-size: 18px;
    line-height: 1;
    padding: 2px;
    transition: color .15s;
  }
  .btn-del:hover { color: var(--error); }

  .empty-state {
    text-align: center;
    padding: 40px 20px;
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 14px;
  }

  /* ── IMPORT ── */
  .import-strip {
    background: #fff;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 16px 20px;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }
  .import-strip span { font-size: 13px; color: var(--muted); }
  .btn-ghost {
    background: none;
    border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
    color: var(--ink);
    padding: 7px 14px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 500;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: border-color .15s;
  }
  .btn-ghost:hover { border-color: var(--accent); color: var(--accent); }
  #csv-input { display: none; }

  /* ── SEND BAR ── */
  .send-bar {
    position: fixed;
    bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
    background: var(--ink);
    border-top: 3px solid var(--gold);
    padding: 14px 32px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    gap: 16px;
    z-index: 100;
  }
  .send-bar .count { color: rgba(255,255,255,0.6); font-size: 13px; }
  .send-bar .count strong { color: #fff; }

  .btn-send {
    background: var(--gold);
    color: var(--ink);
    border: none;
    padding: 11px 28px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-family: var(--sans);
    font-size: 14px;
    font-weight: 700;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity .15s;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 8px;
  }
  .btn-send:hover:not(:disabled) { opacity: .85; }
  .btn-send:disabled { opacity: .5; cursor: not-allowed; }

  /* ── LOG ── */
  .log {
    background: var(--ink);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 16px;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    font-size: 12px;
    max-height: 200px;
    overflow-y: auto;
    margin-bottom: 80px;
    display: none;
  }
  .log.visible { display: block; }
  .log-line { padding: 2px 0; }
  .log-line.ok  { color: #4ADE80; }
  .log-line.err { color: #F87171; }
  .log-line.inf { color: #93C5FD; }

  /* ── TOAST ── */
  #toast {
    position: fixed;
    top: 20px; right: 20px;
    padding: 12px 18px;
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    z-index: 999;
    opacity: 0;
    transform: translateY(-8px);
    transition: opacity .25s, transform .25s;
    pointer-events: none;
    max-width: 320px;
  }
  #toast.show { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
  #toast.success { background: var(--success-bg); color: var(--success); border: 1px solid #BBF7D0; }
  #toast.error   { background: var(--error-bg);   color: var(--error);   border: 1px solid #FECACA; }
  #toast.warn    { background: var(--warn-bg);     color: var(--warn);    border: 1px solid #FDE68A; }

  /* ── PROGRESS ── */
  .progress-bar-wrap {
    height: 3px;
    background: rgba(255,255,255,.15);
    border-radius: 2px;
    flex: 1;
    display: none;
  }
  .progress-bar-wrap.visible { display: block; }
  .progress-bar-fill {
    height: 100%;
    background: var(--gold);
    border-radius: 2px;
    transition: width .3s;
    width: 0%;
  }

  /* ── TEMPLATE PREVIEW ── */
  .preview-toggle {
    font-size: 12px;
    color: var(--accent);
    cursor: pointer;
    text-decoration: underline;
    margin-top: 8px;
    display: inline-block;
  }
  .preview-box {
    display: none;
    margin-top: 12px;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: var(--radius);
    padding: 16px;
    background: #FAFAF8;
    font-size: 13px;
    line-height: 1.7;
    white-space: pre-wrap;
    font-family: var(--mono);
    color: var(--ink);
  }
  .preview-box.visible { display: block; }
</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
  <div class="eyebrow">Themis Vanguard · LASUASA IEC</div>
  <h1>Screening Schedule Mailer</h1>
  <p>Send personalised screening date &amp; time notifications to each aspirant</p>
</header>

<div class="shell">

  <!-- CONFIG -->
  <div class="config-card">
    <h2>Brevo API Config</h2>
    <div class="field-row">
      <div class="field full">
        <label>Brevo API Key</label>
        <input type="password" id="api-key" placeholder="xkeysib-…" />
      </div>
      <div class="field full">
        <label>Sender Name</label>
        <input type="text" id="sender-name" value="LASUASA IEC — Themis Vanguard" />
      </div>
      <div class="field full">
        <label>Sender Email</label>
        <input type="email" id="sender-email" value="lasuasaiec@gmail.com" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- EMAIL TEMPLATE -->
  <div class="config-card">
    <h2>Email Template</h2>
    <div class="field-row">
      <div class="field full">
        <label>Subject Line</label>
        <input type="text" id="email-subject" value="LASUASA Screening Notice — Your Scheduled Date & Time" />
      </div>
      <div class="field full">
        <label>Email Body — use <code style="font-size:11px;background:#eee;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px">{{name}}</code>, <code style="font-size:11px;background:#eee;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px">{{position}}</code>, <code style="font-size:11px;background:#eee;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px">{{date}}</code>, <code style="font-size:11px;background:#eee;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px">{{time}}</code>, <code style="font-size:11px;background:#eee;padding:1px 4px;border-radius:3px">{{venue}}</code></label>
        <textarea id="email-body">Dear {{name}},

We write to officially inform you that your screening for the position of {{position}} has been scheduled as follows:

  📅  Date:    {{date}}
  🕐  Time:    {{time}}
  📍  Venue:   {{venue}}

Please ensure you arrive at least 15 minutes before your scheduled time with all required documents. Failure to appear at the stated time may result in disqualification.

For enquiries, contact the IEC at lasuasaiec@gmail.com.

Regards,
LASUASA Independent Electoral Committee (IEC)
Themis Vanguard</textarea>
        <span class="preview-toggle" onclick="togglePreview()">Preview sample email ▾</span>
        <pre class="preview-box" id="preview-box"></pre>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- VENUE (global default) -->
  <div class="config-card">
    <h2>Default Venue</h2>
    <div class="field-row">
      <div class="field full">
        <label>Venue / Location (used if not set per-row)</label>
        <input type="text" id="default-venue" placeholder="e.g. Architecture Studio, LASU Epe Campus" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- IMPORT -->
  <div class="import-strip">
    <span>Add aspirants manually below, or import a CSV</span>
    <button class="btn-ghost" onclick="document.getElementById('csv-input').click()">⬆ Import CSV</button>
    <input type="file" id="csv-input" accept=".csv" onchange="importCSV(this)" />
    <button class="btn-ghost" onclick="downloadTemplate()">⬇ Download CSV Template</button>
  </div>

  <!-- TABLE -->
  <div class="table-header">
    <h2>Aspirants ({{count}})</h2>
    <button class="btn-add" onclick="addRow()">＋ Add Aspirant</button>
  </div>

  <div class="aspirants-table">
    <div class="tbl-head">
      <span>Full Name</span>
      <span>Email</span>
      <span>Position</span>
      <span>Date &amp; Time</span>
      <span>Venue Override</span>
      <span></span>
    </div>
    <div id="rows-container">
      <div class="empty-state" id="empty-msg">No aspirants yet. Click <strong>+ Add Aspirant</strong> or import a CSV.</div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- LOG -->
  <div class="log" id="log"></div>

</div><!-- .shell -->

<!-- SEND BAR -->
<div class="send-bar">
  <div class="count"><strong id="bar-count">0</strong> aspirant(s) loaded</div>
  <div class="progress-bar-wrap" id="prog-wrap">
    <div class="progress-bar-fill" id="prog-fill"></div>
  </div>
  <button class="btn-send" id="send-btn" onclick="sendAll()" disabled>
    ✉ Send Schedule Emails
  </button>
</div>

<div id="toast"></div>

<script>
  const rows = [];
  let sending = false;

  /* ── ROW MANAGEMENT ── */
  function addRow(data = {}) {
    // Use integer id to avoid floating decimals in attribute generation
    const id = Date.now() + Math.floor(Math.random() * 1000000);
    rows.push({ id, name: data.name || '', email: data.email || '', position: data.position || '', datetime: data.datetime || '', venue: data.venue || '' });
    renderRows();
  }

  function removeRow(id) {
    const i = rows.findIndex(r => r.id === id);
    if (i > -1) rows.splice(i, 1);
    renderRows();
  }

  function updateRow(id, field, value) {
    const r = rows.find(r => r.id === id);
    if (r) {
      if (field === 'email') value = String(value || '').trim();
      r[field] = value;
    }
    updateBarCount();
  }

  function renderRows() {
    const container = document.getElementById('rows-container');
    const empty = document.getElementById('empty-msg');

    if (rows.length === 0) {
      container.innerHTML = '';
      container.appendChild(empty);
      empty.style.display = '';
      updateBarCount();
      return;
    }
    empty.style.display = 'none';

    // Rebuild rows using DOM methods (avoid innerHTML injection issues)
    container.innerHTML = '';
    rows.forEach(r => {
      const row = document.createElement('div');
      row.className = 'aspirant-row';
      row.id = 'row-' + r.id;

      // Column 1: Name + status dot
      const colName = document.createElement('div');
      colName.style.display = 'flex';
      colName.style.alignItems = 'center';
      colName.style.gap = '6px';

      const status = document.createElement('span');
      status.className = 'row-status';
      status.id = 'st-' + r.id;

      const nameInput = document.createElement('input');
      nameInput.type = 'text';
      nameInput.placeholder = 'Full name';
      nameInput.value = r.name || '';
      nameInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => updateRow(r.id, 'name', e.target.value));

      colName.appendChild(status);
      colName.appendChild(nameInput);
      row.appendChild(colName);

      // Column 2: Email
      const colEmail = document.createElement('div');
      const emailInput = document.createElement('input');
      emailInput.type = 'email';
      emailInput.placeholder = 'email@…';
      emailInput.value = r.email || '';
      emailInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => updateRow(r.id, 'email', e.target.value));
      colEmail.appendChild(emailInput);
      row.appendChild(colEmail);

      // Column 3: Position
      const colPos = document.createElement('div');
      const posInput = document.createElement('input');
      posInput.type = 'text';
      posInput.placeholder = 'Position';
      posInput.value = r.position || '';
      posInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => updateRow(r.id, 'position', e.target.value));
      colPos.appendChild(posInput);
      row.appendChild(colPos);

      // Column 4: DateTime
      const colDt = document.createElement('div');
      const dtInput = document.createElement('input');
      dtInput.type = 'datetime-local';
      dtInput.value = r.datetime || '';
      dtInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => updateRow(r.id, 'datetime', e.target.value));
      colDt.appendChild(dtInput);
      row.appendChild(colDt);

      // Column 5: Venue override
      const colVenue = document.createElement('div');
      const venueInput = document.createElement('input');
      venueInput.type = 'text';
      venueInput.placeholder = '(use default)';
      venueInput.value = r.venue || '';
      venueInput.addEventListener('input', (e) => updateRow(r.id, 'venue', e.target.value));
      colVenue.appendChild(venueInput);
      row.appendChild(colVenue);

      // Column 6: Action
      const colAction = document.createElement('div');
      colAction.style.textAlign = 'right';
      const delBtn = document.createElement('button');
      delBtn.className = 'btn-del';
      delBtn.title = 'Remove';
      delBtn.innerHTML = '×';
      delBtn.addEventListener('click', () => removeRow(r.id));
      colAction.appendChild(delBtn);
      row.appendChild(colAction);

      container.appendChild(row);
    });

    updateBarCount();
  }

  function esc(s) { return String(s).replace(/"/g,'&quot;').replace(/</g,'&lt;'); }

  function updateBarCount() {
    document.getElementById('bar-count').textContent = rows.length;
    document.querySelector('.table-header h2').textContent = `Aspirants (${rows.length})`;
    document.getElementById('send-btn').disabled = rows.length === 0 || sending;
  }

  /* ── CSV ── */
  function importCSV(input) {
    const file = input.files[0];
    if (!file) return;
    const reader = new FileReader();
    reader.onload = e => {
      const text = e.target.result.replace(/\r\n/g, '\n').replace(/\r/g, '\n');
      const lines = text.split('\n').filter(l => l.trim().length > 0);
      let skipped = 0;
      // If first line looks like a header, skip it
      const startIndex = (lines.length > 0 && /name|email/i.test(lines[0])) ? 1 : 0;
      for (let i = startIndex; i < lines.length; i++) {
        const line = lines[i];
        const cols = parseCSVLine(line);
        // Allow rows with at least name & email; position/datetime/venue optional
        if (cols.length < 2) { skipped++; continue; }
        addRow({
          name:     (cols[0] || '').trim(),
          email:    (cols[1] || '').trim(),
          position: (cols[2] || '').trim(),
          datetime: (cols[3] || '').trim(),
          venue:    (cols[4] || '').trim(),
        });
      }
      showToast(`Imported ${rows.length} aspirant(s)${skipped ? ` (${skipped} rows skipped)` : ''}`, 'success');
    };
    reader.readAsText(file);
    input.value = '';
  }

  function parseCSVLine(line) {
    // Robust CSV line parser: handles quoted fields, escaped quotes ("")
    const result = [];
    let cur = '';
    let inQuotes = false;
    for (let i = 0; i < line.length; i++) {
      const ch = line[i];
      if (ch === '"') {
        if (inQuotes && line[i+1] === '"') {
          cur += '"'; // escaped quote
          i++;
          continue;
        }
        inQuotes = !inQuotes;
        continue;
      }
      if (ch === ',' && !inQuotes) {
        result.push(cur);
        cur = '';
        continue;
      }
      cur += ch;
    }
    result.push(cur);
    // Trim whitespace and remove stray carriage returns
    return result.map(s => s.replace(/\r$/, '').trim());
  }

  function downloadTemplate() {
    const csv = `Name,Email,Position,DateTime (YYYY-MM-DDTHH:MM),Venue Override\n` +
      `Babatunde Adeyemi,babatunde@example.com,President,2026-07-10T10:00,Architecture Studio Room 3\n` +
      `Fatima Sule,fatima@example.com,Secretary-General,2026-07-10T11:00,`;
    download('lasuasa_screening_schedule_template.csv', csv, 'text/csv');
  }

  function download(name, content, type) {
    const a = document.createElement('a');
    a.href = URL.createObjectURL(new Blob([content], { type }));
    a.download = name;
    a.click();
  }

  /* ── EMAIL TEMPLATE ── */
  const LASU_LOGO    = 'data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAN0AAADkCAYAAAAcsSF/AAEAAElEQVR4nOy9d5xlx1nn/a2qk2/uOLEna0YaaZRGOUdbliUbB6KNvQYvYUm7wC77AuY1YRezwLu7wMKSWQwGbJOccLZkBStaWZqcZzpMd9[...]';
  const LASUASA_LOGO = 'data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAAtAAAAKwCAYAAACxo0jGAAEAAElEQVR4nOz9abMkyZUliJ17Vc3Mt7dHvNj3zIzcsQO1AKitq4Uz0xRyRErIT+RPIykUyvADPwyHHIrMNKuH3VVdqAIKayKB3JFbREbG8u[...]';

  function buildEmail(r) {
    const dt = r.datetime ? new Date(r.datetime) : null;
    const dateStr = dt ? dt.toLocaleDateString('en-NG', { weekday:'long', year:'numeric', month:'long', day:'numeric' }) : '(date not set)';
    const timeStr = dt ? dt.toLocaleTimeString('en-NG', { hour:'2-digit', minute:'2-digit', hour12:true }) : '(time not set)';
    const venue   = r.venue?.trim() || document.getElementById('default-venue').value.trim() || 'TBC';

    const bodyText = document.getElementById('email-body').value
      .replace(/\{\{name\}\}/g,     r.name     || '')
      .replace(/\{\{position\}\}/g, r.position || '')
      .replace(/\{\{date\}\}/g,     dateStr)
      .replace(/\{\{time\}\}/g,     timeStr)
      .replace(/\{\{venue\}\}/g,    venue);

    const subject = document.getElementById('email-subject').value
      .replace(/\{\{name\}\}/g,     r.name     || '')
      .replace(/\{\{position\}\}/g, r.position || '');

    const bodyHtml = bodyText
      .split('\n')
      .map(line => line.trim() === '' ? '<br/>' : `<p style="margin:0 0 8px 0;">${line}</p>`)
      .join('');

    const htmlContent = `<!DOCTYPE html>
<html><head><meta charset="UTF-8"/></head>
<body style="margin:0;padding:0;background:#f4f4f4;font-family:Arial,sans-serif;">
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f4f4f4;padding:24px 0;">
<tr><td align="center">
<table width="600" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#fff;border-radius:8px;overflow:hidden;box-shadow:0 2px 12px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);max-width:600px;width:100%;">
<tr><td style="background:#1a4d2e;padding:24px 32px;border-bottom:4px solid #C9A84C;">
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0"><tr>
<td width="70" align="center"><img src="${LASU_LOGO}" alt="LASU" width="60" height="60" style="display:block;object-fit:contain;"/></td>
<td align="center" style="padding:0 12px;">
  <div style="font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#C9A84C;font-weight:600;margin-bottom:4px;">Themis Vanguard &middot; LASUASA IEC</div>
  <div style="font-size:18px;font-weight:700;color:#fff;line-height:1.2;">Screening Schedule Notice</div>
</td>
<td width="70" align="center"><img src="${LASUASA_LOGO}" alt="LASUASA" width="60" height="60" style="display:block;object-fit:contain;"/></td>
</tr></table>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:28px 36px;color:#0c1320;font-size:14px;line-height:1.7;">${bodyHtml}</td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:0 36px 28px;">
<table width="100%" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="background:#f0fdf4;border:1px solid #86efac;border-radius:6px;overflow:hidden;">
<tr><td style="background:#1a4d2e;padding:10px 18px;"><span style="color:#C9A84C;font-size:11px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.12em;text-transform:uppercase;">Screening Details</span></td></tr>
<tr><td style="padding:16px 18px;">
<table cellpadding="6" cellspacing="0">
<tr><td style="font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;padding-right:16px;">&#128197; Date</td><td style="font-size:14px;color:#0c1320;font-weight:700;">${dateStr}</td></tr>
<tr><td style="font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;padding-right:16px;">&#128336; Time</td><td style="font-size:14px;color:#0c1320;font-weight:700;">${timeStr}</td></tr>
<tr><td style="font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;padding-right:16px;">&#128205; Venue</td><td style="font-size:14px;color:#0c1320;font-weight:700;">${venue}</td></tr>
<tr><td style="font-size:13px;color:#6b7280;font-weight:600;padding-right:16px;">&#127919; Position</td><td style="font-size:14px;color:#0c1320;font-weight:700;">${r.position || ''}</td></tr>
</table>
</td></tr>
</table>
</td></tr>
<tr><td style="background:#122f1c;padding:16px 32px;border-top:2px solid #C9A84C;text-align:center;">
<p style="margin:0;font-size:11px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.5);">
<strong style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.8);">LASUASA Independent Electoral Committee</strong><br/>
Themis Vanguard &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; lasuasaiec@gmail.com</p>
