  "Shambakiu Ramadan","shambakiu@example.com","President","2026-07-10T10:00","Architecture, Studio"
  This will correctly parse the comma in venue and the full name/email.
- Click "＋ Add Aspirant" — a new editable row should appear immediately.
- Fill in name and email; try an invalid email like "bob@" — sending will skip that row and log the reason.
- Check browser console for console.log/console.error messages that explain what happened; the in-page log (black box) also shows progress.

